title: LA Releases First Single SHOWTIME
text:
By MusicDish
LA Releases First Single SHOWTIME
Saturday, October 7, 2017 15:06
% of readers think this story is Fact. Add your two cents.
LA, a 20 year old artist, has a lot of talent: pop singer, musician, composer, fashion model and visual artist.  She includes American Sign Language (ASL) in her choreography and you can find her LA stickers everywhere in Paris.  LA has just released her first single SHOWTIME, and has already announced her next : MISTER PRESIDENT to be released mid September.  Absolutely an artist to follow!  Website: http://www.la-official.com  Source: http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=199440
